xTc " style=3D"font-variant: normal;"> for 1 only by the concept of words b=
eing differed by tones, a concept that is quite strange to an English speak=
er. Tones in Chinese are also the only way the words for "</span><a class=
=3D"XqQF9c" href=3D"https://sites.google.com/site/pointlesslargenumberstuff=
/home/l/pgln1/4" style=3D"color: inherit; text-decoration: none;"><span cla=
