;">" and "death" are distinguished, leading to 4's connotation of bad luck =
in Chinese culture.</span></p><p dir=3D"ltr" class=3D"zfr3Q CDt4Ke " style=
=3D""><span class=3D"C9DxTc " style=3D"font-variant: normal;">Counting to 1=
00 million would take 9 years non-stop, but that=E2=80=99s unrealistic. It=
=E2=80=99s hard to say whether people have reached 100 million by cointing =
or not. Light moves at 300 million meters per second. America=E2=80=99s pop=
ulation is around 300 million. The moon is 400 million meters from the Eart=
h.</span></p><p dir=3D"ltr" class=3D"zfr3Q CDt4Ke " style=3D""><span class=
=3D"C9DxTc " style=3D"font-variant: normal;">In the -yllion naming system (=
