angnam Style</span></a><span class=3D"C9DxTc " style=3D"font-variant: norma=
l;">, the only one with 2 billion or more). The number of webpages in the w=
hole huge seemingly endless Internet is in the billions. India has a popula=
tion of around a billion.</span></p><p dir=3D"ltr" class=3D"zfr3Q CDt4Ke " =
style=3D""><span class=3D"C9DxTc " style=3D"font-variant: normal;">So a bil=
lion is definitely a pretty big number alright, isn=E2=80=99t it? It can de=
