ube is - it's a puzzle made of 26 little cubes connected with a center piec=
e, where the goal is to configure it such that each face has only one color=
. The puzzle looks deceptively simple, but it's actually quite a difficult =
puzzle if you don't know the trick to solve it. That little cube turns out =
to have 43 </span><span class=3D"C9DxTc " style=3D"font-style: italic; font=
